com.algolia.search.saas

Class RequestOptions

  • Object
    • com.algolia.search.saas.RequestOptions

  • public class RequestOptions
extends Object
    Per-request options. This class allows specifying options at the request level, overriding default options at the Client level. NOTE: These are reserved for advanced use cases. In most situations, they shouldn't be needed.
